'''Jjwaǧ''' neɣ '''zzwaǧ''' neɣ asali s teqbaylit, d asdukel n sin yemdanen deg yiwen wexxam. Asali yettili ger wergaz d tmettut. Tikkal yiwen wergaz d snat neɣ 3 neɣ 4 n tlawin. Acku lislam ddin n yiqbayliyen yifka-yas lḥeq i wargaz akken i yezewǧ 4 n tilawin acku i yessaɛdel gar-asent.

Leqbayel sseqdacen awal asali seg wemyag suli meḥsub zweǧ. Amedya : leflani yessuli axxam, meḥsub yezweǧ, yuɣ tamettut.

Win neɣ tin ara yessalin neqqar-as isli, tislit . asegt islan, tislatin.
